item.description:
1. install dependencies 1  $ yum install -y gcc-c++ pcre pcre-devel zlib zlib-devel openssl openssl-devel   2. make dir 1 2 3 4  $ mkdir /usr/setup $ mkdir /opt/package $ mkdir /usr/setup/nginx $ mkdir /usr/setup/nginx/temp   3. download and upload download tar resource file &lsquo;nginx-1.12.2.tar.gz&rsquo;
upload to &lsquo;/opt/package/&rsquo;
4. intall 4.1 release this tar file 1 2  $ tar zxf nginx-1.12.2.tar.gz $ cd nginx-1.12.2/   4.
